                        <bibl>
                            <ref target="https://papyri.info/biblio/17588">Yiftach-Firanko, U. (2003)</ref> Marriage and Marital Arrangements. A History of the Greek Marriage Document in Egypt. 4th century BCE – 4th century CE, Münchener Beiträge zur Papyrusforschung und antiken Rechtsgeschichte, Heft 93. München.</bibl>
                    </listBibl>
                </div>
            </div>
